            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="features-container">
            <h2 class="features-title">Everything you need for personal conversations</h2>
            <p class="features-subtitle">
                Powerful features designed to make personal communication seamless, private, and enjoyable.
